cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.MA, cs.NA

This paper deals with distributed optimization methods for empirical risk minimization, which is a common problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves optimization and distributed computing, which suggests categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the paper uses mathematical analysis to establish convergence results, which could place it in categories such as cs.MA (Mathematical Optimization) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
